Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka! We're gonna get going pretty soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my dear younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your new life starts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.70,0:01:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with some enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:05.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Under One Roof"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to report Yutaka's \Nacceptance, and to say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Yutaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure I will be causing \Nmany problems from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I give my best regards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of this as your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, congratulations \Non getting accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I'm so glad she got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can be reunited with \Nthat handkerchief girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My life is just that of a winner's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Going back in time"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The day of Yutaka's entrance exams"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to go to the \Nnurse's office with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she called out to me, and \Neven lent me her handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy because I think I'll \Nhave a very good friend now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Yutaka, she might not get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! People like \Nthat are sure to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she's smart too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the completely \Nbaseless counter-argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if \Nyou don't get in, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that there is that possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure that if it's you, \NYu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you'd be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Maybe I'll get to \Nsee her one way or the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the day they announce who got in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to return the handkerchief to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Acceptances and rejections \Nwill both be notified by mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"And..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Orientation and Uniform Fitting Day"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to return \Nthis to you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to deliver this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I troubled you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I would see you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had intended to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought that I wouldn't get accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're here now \Nmeans we're in the same grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... you had thought that \NI was a family member
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of someone taking the entrance exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family is picking me up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my best regards \Nfor the next three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making such a wonderful friend \Nin high school already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to ask her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you see her again, make \Nsure to ask for her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, are you feeling sick, by chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I think I got a bit carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I took medication...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka really is a frail girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, while that's indeed the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, recognize that it's \Nalso partly your driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It even gets to me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the only one going to \NRyouou from my junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get sick really easily like today, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm worried on whether or not \NI'll get to know my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka, you're a good girl, \Nso it'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're treating me like a little child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:36.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Weak from illnesses + sister element \N+ pure + cute = walking {\i1}moe {\i0}factor"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conversion in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, if you teamed \Nup with our Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it would be something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm already at \NKonata-{\i1}oneechan{\i0}'s house now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up so early, even on a holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I'm about to go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was up all night playing 'net games...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My living conditions really did change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally going to be facing \Ncollege entrance exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the cram schools and textbook \Nsalespeople are calling lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you can tell it's \Nthose calls if you get Caller ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those types of calls usually have \Ntheir numbers as "restricted."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caller ID, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been some trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, we're like that ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, since my daughter is back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, then on another occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed like you were having \Na lively conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a salesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, didn't you mention \Nthat you could recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those types of calls right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit bored, so I wanted \Nto have a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up talking for over an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For both items together, the total is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about winning \Nthe national championship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, the world is always \Nat war. There's no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, there was a point-reward \Nitem that I kinda wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about playing offense or defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the end redeemed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, there's a new item \Nout that I want right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that one over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough points \Nleft! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really enjoy life, don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, your total...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you like, \Nsmoking, or non-smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, since we're underage,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd like the non-smoking seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to go to the bathroom first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I always think about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why are bathrooms in places like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,often located on the same \Nside as the smoking seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out of our way to \Npick the non-smoking seats, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, I wonder why that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's because it's \Nbetter to be closer to water
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in case someone causes a fire or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have buckets and hoses and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they have hoses too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do. Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why people who never \Ncontribute any labor to society
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are so troublesome. Oh, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like putting a lid on a bad odor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, let's stop this \Nconversation during a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad smells and toilets and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, in the metropolitan area, \Nthere has been a series of incidents
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where elementary school girls \Nwere called over from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a stranger while on their way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:54.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminal cases that target children \Nhave been on the rise lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The academic committee informed \Nall schools to be on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful too, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I have to say I can \Nunderstand how he feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making such a big deal \Nof it every day like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad to think that there is someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would still call over \Nchildren they don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to say one thing to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Aren't you jealous of me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're thinking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please don't do anything that \Nwould get Sis Yui to arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoohoo! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Kagami today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's out with friends from her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... somehow... frustrating, \Nor rather, a bit lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lonely, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten really warm lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no homework during spring \Nbreak, so it's so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A line like that is reserved for \Nsomeone who always does their best
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to finish her homework by herself, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hit somewhere strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when you play \Nrobot games like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you know who all the \Ncharacters are and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to a certain extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that your tastes in manga and anime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:40.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely burnt out, \Nand turned into white ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been affected by your \Ndad, come to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when you were young,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you weren't able to keep up with all \Nthe conversations that girls had?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I had more chances \Nto see that kind of stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could totally keep up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Uh... Is that so? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your final answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my final answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pause... It really gets to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face is scary, and it's so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Iooking at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she got this question wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit using the time left until the commercial
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to guess whether they got the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't bear all the suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They drag it on for so long, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is all about enjoying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so like Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you. This \Nis my cousin, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you. My \Nname is Yutaka Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends, Tsukasa and Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these two are the ones that \NSis is always talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I wonder what she says about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of stuff have you been telling her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I can tell from her reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Isn't it just like I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, are you done with \Nyour graduation ceremony already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, it was the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduation! That really takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember my graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, did you get the second \Nbutton from the top from any guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our junior high uniform tops were blazers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, lots of \Nschools are like that these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe they don't do all the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"receive something from the person \Nyou're interested in" stuff anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? That's a bit lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I didn't do any of that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at blogs on the 'net,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's still some of it \Ngoing on, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all about getting something \Nfrom the guy you like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at the point that you go to get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're basically confessing your love to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you ask him out properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get the actual person, \Nand not just a button?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the ideal, if \Nyou talk about ideals...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Yutaka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, weren't you \Ninterested in someone or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to stay home from school sick a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even when I attended, I \Nwould get sick really soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really dragged down the \Natmosphere around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm really short, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my physique is so childish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People always used to make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like falling in love with \Nsomeone, or someone falling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, as long \Nas you don't choose your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a big need for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Po-cky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, let me see your yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanna see the yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in that many pictures, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What class were you in, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked at the round circles they use for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people who were absent on picture \Nday before you asked, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you figured that out after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference between junior \Nhigh and high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, where you're not forced \Nto join an extracurricular club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that depend on your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a prep school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the curriculum may be wider and \Nmore fast-paced than in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it takes time to commute to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it will take a bit of stamina, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One definite difference would \Nbe that the farther you move up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from elementary to junior \Nhigh to high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that you spend more \Ntime sleeping in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially on the subjects \Nyou're not good at!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that might be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher starts sounding like \Nthey're talking a different language,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure that you \Ndon't end up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when that happens your \Nconsciousness starts to drift away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you brought \Nyour junior high uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Our uniform was pretty plain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd be able to \Nwear it as street clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since this isn't my home area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, what did you guys do \Nwith your uniforms and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave them to younger \Ngirls in our neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure you couldn't \Nfind anyone to give yours to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, I'm like Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, and took the \Neffort to keep it for cosplay purposes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way, \Nit sounds really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in any case, our alma mater...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we talk about stuff like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes me want to drop by my \Nelementary or junior high and say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there have been a lot of run-ins \Nand strange campus visitation cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would be bad to be misunderstood \Nand get weird looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in your case, you won't \Nhave to worry about that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right in assuming \Nthat wasn't a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But vacation sure passes by quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Before you know it, \Nschool's about to start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring has those physical exams \Nand fitness tests of all sorts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you have good \Nmotor nerves. I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which nerves are the motor nerves, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, but Yutaka, \Ncongratulations on graduating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're celebrating a graduation today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's all go drinking together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll invite Uncle, too! It'll be my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis... No, that's not good, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Officer, we're still underage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:09.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do that, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I don't think we can \Ngo in places like that yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't catch on if you go \Nin with your head held up high!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do it all the time \Nback when I was a student,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I was never caught once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, we can't possibly do that, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:27.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure they'll catch on, mostly \Nthanks to your two relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}is with us, \Nwanna go to Land for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's spring vacation, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm very happy about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since I'm imposing \Non you by staying here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to worry about me so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And actually, I went there the \Nother day as a school field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come to think of it, I had \Na field trip like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, were you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My health kept up \Nwith me, and it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with my friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... More like the height \Nrestrictions on the rides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things! I was fine! \NI'm in high school now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so... I was thinking as I was \Nwatching those school drama series,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,junior high and high school are \Ndifferent in all sorts of ways, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have class meals \Nin high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly your own lunches, or \Nmeals at the school cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, and buying boxed lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you make lunch every day, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like things will \Nbe tough from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really good at games and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a very wide range of communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can cook and do household chores!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:18:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I'm starting to understand the \Npressure you feel as an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she looks at me like that, \NI've got to give it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis Yui driving the car recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! You doin' good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis Yui getting drunk and coming \Nback to her family home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homework? It's fine as long \Nas you write something vague!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis Yui being rather irresponsible \Nfor all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I wonder if it all \Ndepends on the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, talk so I can understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my final answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously can't put up with all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,She's irritated today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I finally got around to showing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I checked the recording, \NI'm not on screen at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it... Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they thinking \Nwhen they make the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to fall behind all those \Nidiots who have no sense or talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, call the title! Call the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Please call the title...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes are so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning luckies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! I'm disgusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just my voice, just my voice! \NThere's no point in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I wasn't on screen, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, did I ask about you right now? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I bring you up even this much \Nin the conversation right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... No, not one word about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you stick your face in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you come sauntering out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always, always butt in \Nwith your me-me-me thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call self-centered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just stay back! Someone \Nas lowly as you, Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my mouth is going to rot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, okay? The problem at \Nhand is that I, Akira Kogami,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was not shown on screen in the main segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask you, what am I? I'm an idol, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you mention an idol, \Nyour face is your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about showing up on \Nscreen... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the staff for this episode \Ndid is completely inexcusable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:13.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Akira Kogami" "Revenge" "Plan for a perfect \Nappearance in the main segment!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Akira is asking of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that Akira can show \Nup in the main segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone's help is necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, putting it straight, \NI'd like your support!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any method is okay! In any case, \Njust keep pushing harder and harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want you to see Akira's fine acting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a top-rate actress in the main segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, speaking just between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A "want" call...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comparing the other cast members \Nto the charm of me, Akira,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a giant wall as big as that between
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an Oscar-winning Hollywood actress \Nand a kindergarten class skit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there, that wants to see lots \Nof that pretty, gorgeous acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance is right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overlook it! Your one letter! \NYour one homepage comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come true with Akira in \Nthe main segment of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when this broadcast is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should get a postcard \Nready, or your computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:54.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why are you \Nchit-chatting with me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell \Nyou to not get in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Already? Oh, I wanted all of you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so much more about how fabulous Akira is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you all lots of my true \Ncharm next week in the main segment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Please look forward \Nto the next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's over. It's so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, get the producer over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, this week's \Ncorrected script is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the title of this segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, it's {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The script said "Lucky Paradise."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore! They have some \Nnerve to treat me that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because the previous \Nshow he worked on was a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the producer getting \Nfull of it? Like, full of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:42.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I think you shouldn't be \Nsaying something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Miyagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! This is Minoru Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.50,0:21:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I'd like you to listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I was spending my days \Nwishing for excitement ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Who was it that granted my wish? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A future that you seemingly \N(can predict) but can't ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Even then, I know one thing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ To the end of time, BOOOON! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ This feeling that \Nis a warp and a loop ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ With an imagination that engulfs \Nanything and everything, let's play ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Something on one sunny day, more \Nfun than any magic possible ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.25,0:22:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Endlessly pours down, \Nit's not impossible ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ When we see each other tomorrow, \Nwe're all humming as we smile ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Let's gather happiness, \Nsuch a thing is so easy ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Chase after me, try to catch it ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A big dream... You \Nlike dreams, right? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.11,0:23:13.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The End"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's up with the \Nnext episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.04,0:23:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Minami Iwasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yutaka Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}, apparently the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to introduce the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what it's about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really? That's rather troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll wrap it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: I Can't Suddenly Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't said anything. \NI wonder if it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
